Jamison Newlander https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jamison_Newlander 0 Jamison Newlander (born April 2, 1970) is an American actor who attended New York University. He starred in the 1987 horror film The Lost Boys, playing Alan Frog a vampire hunter. Jamison_Newlander ( born April_2_,_1970 ) is an_American_actor who attended New_York_University .
